     1|/**
     2| * IVX Enterprise Investor Protection System — API handlers.
     3| *
     4| * Owner-only routes (require assertIVXOwnerOnly):
     5| *   GET    /api/ivx/protection/dashboard           → owner controls dashboard (section 8 + 12)
     6| *   GET    /api/ivx/protection/audit-log           → audit log (section 9)
     7| *   GET    /api/ivx/protection/account-states      → list account states (section 2)
     8| *   POST   /api/ivx/protection/account-states/transition → transition state (section 2)
     9| *   POST   /api/ivx/protection/account/unlock      → unlock a verified investor (section 1 + 2)
    10| *   GET    /api/ivx/protection/deletion-requests   → list deletion requests (section 2)
    11| *   POST   /api/ivx/protection/deletion-requests   → create deletion request
    12| *   POST   /api/ivx/protection/deletion-requests/approve   → owner approval
    13| *   POST   /api/ivx/protection/deletion-requests/confirm  → second confirmation
    14| *   GET    /api/ivx/protection/recovery            → list recovery requests (section 1)
    15| *   POST   /api/ivx/protection/recovery/start      → start recovery (email/sms/2fa/admin)
    16| *   POST   /api/ivx/protection/recovery/verify     → verify code
    17| *   POST   /api/ivx/protection/recovery/complete   → admin-assisted complete
    18| *   GET    /api/ivx/protection/sessions            → list sessions (section 1)
    19| *   POST   /api/ivx/protection/sessions/register   → register session
    20| *   POST   /api/ivx/protection/sessions/revoke     → revoke session
    21| *   GET    /api/ivx/protection/investments         → list investments (section 4)
    22| *   POST   /api/ivx/protection/investments         → create investment
    23| *   POST   /api/ivx/protection/investments/valuation → update valuation + profit
    24| *   GET    /api/ivx/protection/withdrawals         → list withdrawals (section 6)
    25| *   POST   /api/ivx/protection/withdrawals         → create withdrawal request
    26| *   POST   /api/ivx/protection/withdrawals/transition → advance withdrawal workflow
    27| *   GET    /api/ivx/protection/wires               → list wires (safe view) (section 7)
    28| *   POST   /api/ivx/protection/wires               → create wire (encrypted)
    29| *   POST   /api/ivx/protection/wires/transition    → transition wire status
    30| *   GET    /api/ivx/protection/wire-queue          → wires pending initiation
    31| *   GET    /api/ivx/protection/compliance          → list compliance records (section 11)
    32| *   GET    /api/ivx/protection/compliance?userId=  → single compliance record
    33| *   POST   /api/ivx/protection/compliance          → upsert compliance
    34| *   GET    /api/ivx/protection/wallet?userId=      → investor wallet summary (section 3)
    35| *   GET    /api/ivx/protection/reports?type=       → owner reports (section 12)
    36| *   POST   /api/ivx/protection/reports             → generate owner report
    37| *   GET    /api/ivx/protection/ledger-integrity    → verify hash-chain ledger (section 5 + 10)
    38| */
